OL,3,CSchoolboy attacked teacher with a
OL,4,Chammer in a 'sort of rage', court hears
OL,6,FA teacher has told a court a student
OL,7,Fbludgeoned him with a hammer as he
OL,8,Fwent to investigate noises coming from
OL,9,Fa boarding house in the middle of the
OL,10,Fnight.
OL,12,FHenry Roffe-Silvester was struck six
OL,13,Ftimes. A 17-year-old student at
OL,14,FBlundell's School in Tiverton, who was
OL,15,F16 at the time, is accused of carrying
OL,16,Fout the attack.
