OL,3,CSchoolboy attacked teacher with a
OL,4,Chammer in a 'sort of rage', court hears
OL,6,FThe court heard how the housemaster
OL,7,Fwas awoken by footsteps coming from
OL,8,Fthe dormitory directly above his
OL,9,Fquarters shortly before 1am on June 9
OL,10,Flast year.
OL,12,FAs Mr Roffe-Silvester entered the
OL,13,Fpitch-black room, he said he saw a
OL,14,Fsilhouetted figure standing in front
OL,15,Fof him who then turned and repeatedly
OL,16,Fhit him over the head with one of
OL,17,Fthree hammers.
