OL,6,FThe maths teacher said all six blows
OL,7,Fhe suffered were directed towards his
OL,8,Fhead and he tried to reassure the
OL,9,Fdefendant that it was him, rather than
OL,10,Fan intruder.
OL,12,F"At this point, I knew it was the
OL,13,Fdefendant," he said.
OL,15,F"I was telling him that it's me in the
OL,16,Fdoorway and not someone else."
OL,18,F"I am going backwards down the
OL,19,Fcorridor with the defendant coming
OL,20,Ftowards me still and trying to hit me
OL,21,Fwith the hammer again.
