OL,6,F"In hindsight, I know I was hit six
OL,7,Ftimes, but I only knew that once I got
OL,8,Fto hospital, I don't really remember
OL,9,Fwhere each of the blows was."
OL,11,FMr Roffe-Silvester said he managed to
OL,12,Fget the hammer from the defendant `
OL,13,Fwho then slumped down in the corridor
OL,14,F` as if squatting.
OL,16,F"I was definitely shouting for help at
OL,17,Fthat point ` I don't remember the
OL,18,Fexact words," he said.
