OL,3,CSchoolboy attacked teacher with a
OL,4,Chammer in a 'sort of rage', court hears
OL,6,FHe told the jury that once the
OL,7,Fhousemaster got the hammer, the
OL,8,Fdemeanour of the defendant, who was
OL,9,Fwearing just his boxer shorts, changed.
OL,11,F"At that point suddenly the
OL,12,Fdefendant's demeanour changed
OL,13,Fsignificantly from being a sort of
OL,14,Frage to calm, as I would normally see
OL,15,Fhim," he said.
OL,17,F"At that point, he slumped down by the
OL,18,Fdoor frame onto his haunches like in a
OL,19,Fsquat position."
