OL,3,CSchoolboy attacked teacher with a
OL,4,Chammer in a 'sort of rage', court hears
OL,6,FHe told the jury he asked another boy
OL,7,Fto stay with the defendant and he
OL,8,Fheard the defendant tell that boy: "I
OL,9,Fwas dreaming" and "(an alleged victim)
OL,10,Fhad a hammer".
OL,12,FMr Roffe-Silvester told the court he
OL,13,Fwas then called to the dormitory by
OL,14,Fother teenagers who had discovered the
OL,15,Ftwo boys lying in their beds severely
OL,16,Finjured.
OL,18,F"I first saw one of the boys... the
OL,19,Fmost immediate thing is the amount of
OL,20,Fblood everywhere," he said.
