OL,3,CSchoolboy attacked teacher with a
OL,4,Chammer in a 'sort of rage', court hears
OL,6,F"There was a large pool of blood on
OL,7,Fthe floor to the left of his bed and
OL,8,Fthere was a lot of blood on his desk
OL,9,Fand on the floor.
OL,11,F"I first see him in his bed and he's
OL,12,Fin a sleeping position lying down and
OL,13,Fhe's covered in blood and there's no
OL,14,Fduvet on him."
OL,16,FMr Roffe-Silvester said the other boy
OL,17,Fwas also lying on his bed covered in
OL,18,Fblood and was making groaning noises.
OL,20,F"The blood was less on him and more
OL,21,Fcontained within the bed."
