OL,3,CSchoolboy attacked teacher with a
OL,4,Chammer in a 'sort of rage', court hears
OL,6,FBoth boys suffered skull fractures, as
OL,7,Fwell as injuries to their ribs,
OL,8,Fspleen, a punctured lung and internal
OL,9,Fbleeding.
OL,11,FThe jury heard Mr Roffe-Silvester did
OL,12,Fnot have his phone with him and
OL,13,Fanother student called the emergency
OL,14,Fservices.
OL,16,FHe said he found two hammers in the
OL,17,Froom and put them with the hammer he
OL,18,Fhad taken from the defendant in his
OL,19,Foffice until the police arrived.
